# ========================================================
#            MODDING HUB - MASTER GITIGNORE
# ========================================================

# --- System & OS Garbage ---
# Ignore OS-specific hidden files and temporary clutter
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp
*.bak
desktop.ini

# --- The Development Vault ---
# This ignores your local lab: _Archive, _Workbench, _Library, _Automation...
# These files are backed up via your .bat script but stay off GitHub.
**/_Vault/

# --- Starbound Specifics ---
# Ignore Steam config files, local saves, and game logs
**/steamtext_info.txt

# --- Out of Scope Projects ---
# Local directories for other games that shouldn't be synced here
/Kenshi/
/ProjectZomboid/
/Valheim/

# --- IDE & Text Editors ---
# Ignore workspace configurations (VS Code, Sublime, IntelliJ)
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Compressed Archives ---
# Do not version control archives; use GitHub Releases for distribution
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z

# ========================================================
#  Note: Only "Project-FR-Core" & main docs are tracked.
# ========================================================